Security in Garissa town was intensified after two terror suspects engaged KDF officers in a gun battle.

The two suspects tried to storm the Garissa KDF camp, armed with guns they marched towards the camp before they were approached by officers. 

They then opened fire at the officers who engaged them in a gun battle. One of them was seriously injured and an AK 47 rifle was recovered. His accomplice escaped but with injuries.

